#!/usr/bin/env python3
# ruff: noqa: F401 -- declarative dependency bindings resolve facade names late
"""Ambient CLI for model-aware ask, audit, map, code, build, and agent work.

Run ``ambient-codex -h`` or a subcommand's ``-h`` for the complete interface.
Large inputs use bounded map-reduce; builds use resumable manifest-first batches
and write only with ``--apply``. Credentials remain private. Concrete models are
never silently replaced; auto/fallback require explicit delegation. Exit codes:
0 ok; 1 error; 2 partial; 3 unconfigured; 64 usage; 130 interrupted. Public
output is token-only; relative savings are opt-in and money is never displayed.
"""

